What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Ibuprofen API Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Ibuprofen API Market

The ibuprofen API market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 4.90% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028 is expected to reach USD 0.570 billion by 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on ibuprofen API market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth. The rise in the prevalence of chronic diseases globally is escalating the growth of ibuprofen API market.

Ibuprofen refers to a medication in the nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drug (NSAID) class which is extensively utilized in the treatment for fever, treating pain and inflammation. The medication is generally taken for migraines, painful menstrual periods and rheumatoid arthritis. This could also be used as a patent ductus arteriosus in a premature baby. It could be taken through mouth or intravenously and generally works within an hour.

The rise in the pharmaceutical and biopharmaceutical production across the globe acts as one of the major factors driving the growth of ibuprofen API market. The increase in the incidences of wide range of diseases such as infectious diseases, diabetes, cardiovascular disease and kidney-related complications and the rise in the need for drug development to treat the diseases efficiently accelerate the ibuprofen API market growth. The high utilization of advanced technologies such as bioinformatics, high throughput and combinatorial chemistry for the identification of better drug further influences the ibuprofen API market. Additionally, emerging technologies, growth in awareness regarding diseases and treatments, changing lifestyle, rise in healthcare expenditure and surge in investment for research projects positively affect the ibuprofen API market. Furthermore, research and development activities extend profitable opportunities to the ibuprofen API market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, the implementations of stringent regulations regarding drugs manufacturing and sales across few regions and fluctuation in demand patterns are the factors expected to obstruct the ibuprofen API market growth. The negative impact of COVID-19 on pharmaceutical and biopharmaceutical sectors among others is projected to challenge the ibuprofen API market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

